          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
      <div class="3u">

        <!-- Feature #2 -->
        <section>
          <a href="#" class="bordered-feature-image"><img src="images/picture5.png" width="262" height="110" alt=""/></a>
          <h2>Outhouses don't have changing tables</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Blog:</strong> As an avid hiker I wanted to share the outdoors with my newborn. But, with a diaper
            bag heavier than my bowling duffle and trying to balance diaper changing in some of nature's
            outhouses, it wasn't fun. Scalene changed that.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
      <div class="3u">

        <!-- Feature #3 -->
        <section>
          <a href="#" class="bordered-feature-image"><img src="images/Picture6.png" width="262" height="110" alt=""/></a>
          <h2>Stories of public restrooms</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Blog:</strong> I'm the dad that boils the toys to disinfect. Imagine my horror when we had our first child
            and I realized most public men's restrooms are less than satisfactory for diaper duty.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
      <div class="3u">

        <!-- Feature #4 -->
        <section>
          <a href="#" class="bordered-feature-image"><img src="images/banner.jpg" width="262" height="110" alt=""/></a>
          <h2>Why I missed the bottom of the 9th</h2>
          <p>
            <strong>Blog:</strong> A family day at the ballpark can turn into a playground when you have four young kids.
            Scalene made it possible for me to take charge of changing diapers without compromising the biggest moments in the game.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Content -->
<div id="content-wrapper">
  <div id="content">
    <div class="5grid">
      <div class="4u-first">

        <!-- Box #1 -->
        <section>
          <header>
            <h2>The only changing pad that won't change you.</h2>
          </header>
          <a href="#" class="feature-image"><img src="images/Picture1.png" width="324" height="126" alt=""/></a>
          <p>
            Hiking? Biking? At the game? Eliminate the search and stress of finding a clean changing table.
