              <p>"Rather than haul a changing blanket up the mountain, this product fits in my back pocket!"</p>
              <span>Jeffrey Maguire, dad and sports fan</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <img src="images/Picture3.png" width="70" height="70" alt=""/>
              <p>"I wish I had this for baby #1."</p>
              <span>Jesse Van Nostrand, father of 4</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

